---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Regalo / Lista Nozze - Claudia & Jacopo | 25 Giugno 2025">
	<section id="regalo" class="py-section-gap-mobile md:py-section-gap-desktop px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
		<div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto">
			<div class="text-center mb-stack-lg">
				<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-5xl inline-block mb-stack-md">favorite</span>
				<h1 class="font-display-lg-mobile md:font-display-lg text-display-lg-mobile md:text-display-lg text-primary mb-stack-sm">Il nostro Regalo più grande</h1>
				<p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl mx-auto italic mb-stack-lg">La vostra presenza nel giorno del nostro sì è il dono più prezioso che potessimo desiderare.</p>				<img src=\"https://placehold.co/800x400/9b3f25/fcf9f2?text=Regalo+per+Voi\" alt=\"Regalo\" class=\"w-full rounded-lg shadow-lg object-cover h-64 md:h-80 mt-stack-lg\" />			</div>

			<div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-stack-lg">
				<div class="form-card p-stack-lg">
					<div class="flex gap-stack-md mb-stack-md">
						<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl flex-shrink-0">favorite</span>
						<div>
							<h2 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface mb-stack-sm">Il nostro Regalo più grande sei Tu</h2>
							<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-stack-md">La vostra presenza nel giorno del nostro sì è il dono più prezioso che potessimo desiderare. Tuttavia, se desiderate partecipare alla realizzazione del nostro sogno di vita insieme o contribuire al nostro viaggio di nozze, qui di seguito trovate i dettagli per farlo.</p>
							<a href="#iban" class="text-primary hover:underline font-body-md text-body-md">Vedi informazioni bonifico</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="form-card p-stack-lg">
					<div class="flex gap-stack-md mb-stack-md">
						<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl flex-shrink-0">account_balance</span>
						<div id="iban">
							<h2 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface mb-stack-md">Bonifico Bancario</h2>
							<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-stack-md">Se desiderate contribuire al nostro viaggio di nozze:</p>
							<div class="bg-surface-container-low p-stack-md rounded-lg mb-stack-md border border-outline-variant/20">
								<p class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-widest mb-stack-sm">Intestatario</p>
								<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface mb-stack-md">Jacopo Guerini e Claudia Merati</p>
								<p class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-widest mb-stack-sm">IBAN</p>
								<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface font-mono mb-stack-md">IT 00 X 00000 00000 0 000000000000</p>
								<button onclick="navigator.clipboard.writeText('IT 00 X 00000 00000 0 000000000000')" class="btn-secondary w-full">
									<span class="material-symbols-outlined">content_copy</span>
									Copia IBAN
								</button>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="form-card p-stack-lg">
					<div class="flex gap-stack-md">
						<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl flex-shrink-0">card_giftcard</span>
						<div>
							<h2 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface mb-stack-md">Lista Nozze</h2>
							<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-stack-md">Potete trovare la nostra lista nozze presso i seguenti store:</p>
							<ul class="space-y-stack-sm">
								<li><a href="#" class="text-primary hover:underline font-body-md text-body-md">→ Giftbox (online)</a></li>
								<li><a href="#" class="text-primary hover:underline font-body-md text-body-md">→ Negozio locale</a></li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="text-center pt-stack-lg">
					<a href="/" class="btn-primary">Torna alla homepage</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

	<style>
		.page-section {
			padding: 24px;
			max-width: 640px;
			margin: 0 auto;
		}

		h1 {
			font-size: 1.75rem;
			margin-bottom: 1rem;
		}

		h2 {
			font-size: 1.25rem;
			margin-top: 1.5rem;
		}

		ul {
			padding-left: 1.25rem;
		}

		a {
			color: inherit;
			text-decoration: underline;
		}
	</style>
